6
00:01:12,310 --> 00:01:13,920
I don't know what kind of person he is.

7
00:01:14,070 --> 00:01:16,150
But I know exactly what kind of person you are now.

8
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:19,590
I found these stockings on your sofa bed.

9
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:22,350
